mic the movements and expressions of its opponents, but it\u2019s still not very good at it."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"When this gifted mimic surprises an opponent, Mime Jr. feels so happy that it ends up forgetting it was imitating something."},{"version":"sword","text":"It mimics everyone it sees, but it puts extra effort into copying the graceful dance steps of Mr. Rime as practice."},{"version":"shield","text":"It looks for a Mr. Rime that\u2019s a good dancer and carefully copies the Mr. Rime\u2019s steps like an apprentice."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"Known to turn up in bustling marketplaces now and again. It mimics people much as a child would, then watches how they react, eyes sparkling."}],"evo":{"name":"mime-jr","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"mr-mime","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":"mimic","known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"mr-rime","level":2,"min_level":42,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/439.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/shiny/439.png","capture":145,"happiness":70,"growth":"medium","gender":4,"hatch":25,"ev":{"special_defense":1},"forms":[]}